The paper discusses security challenges and research opportunities in deep learning methodologies, specifically transfer learning. This involves aspects of computer security (cs.CR) as well as machine learning (cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses vulnerabilities and attacks unique to these methodologies, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE).
